      <h2>Dexelect</h2>
      <p class="text">
        <i>Released 12 December 2025</i>
      </p>

      <img class="portrait" src="/static/images/dexelect-gui.png" />

      <p class="text">
        Dexelect is a progression-aware Pokémon team generator. It can be used to prescribe a randomized (but obtainable) party according to user-specified customizations and restrictions. Fully compatible with Solus RGB (as well as vanilla Gens 1–4).
      </p>

      <ul class="compact-list">
        <li><a href="https://dexelect.derekandersen.net">Use the web app</a></li>
        <li><a href="https://github.com/Dechrissen/dexelect/releases/latest">Download for desktop</a></li>
        <li><a href="https://github.com/Dechrissen/dexelect">GitHub repo</a></li>
      </ul>
      
